      • debugOperationAttemptAsPrincipal

        public String debugOperationAttemptAsPrincipal​(String resource,
                                               String operation,
                                               org.forgerock.services.context.Context context,
                                               String realm,
                                               Debug debug)
        Logs an operation attempt on a resource, pulling the principal's name out of the context passed in, and indicating in which realm the operation is requested (if appropriate).
        Parameters:
        resource - the resource being used. Not nullable.
        operation - the operation on the resource being performed. Not nullable.
        context - the context of the operation request. Not nullable.
        realm - the realm in which we are executing. Nullable.
        debug - the debug to write messages out to. Not nullable.
        Returns:
        the name of the principal which requested the operation, or null if not available.

        Audits an attempted REST request, indicating which resource was accessed using which method linked to the SSOToken of the accessing user.
        Parameters:

        action - The CREST action-type requested.
        token - The SSO token of the accessing user (null if XUI)
